      "$value": "#ff37c7",
      "$type": "color",
      "$description": "Uniswap Pink — Primary brand mark, filled CTA buttons, active nav indicator, and the only chromatic color an interface should use — saturated hot-pink against a white canvas creates instant focal hierarchy without darkening the page"
    },
